Title: Purple Motion #2
Location: Salem, Oregon
Year Taken: 2020
About this photo: At the time, I was experimenting with motion in photographs along with some colorful pizazz. Kyla was down, she thought it was piles of fun! I won’t get into the mechanics here, but I will say that the method we used was tricky. It involved lots and lots of outtakes, things that simply weren’t working. That’s what happens with experimentation!
